{"tid":2370930,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"涉違國安法被捕 前學生動源成員何忻諾、陳渭賢及何諾恆獲准取回護照","createTime":"2021-01-18T11:30:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-18T16:00:02.000Z","uid":240362,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"b8a3200be898b1dee185bbe7e6ef50b58b2873ac","tid":2370930,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T11:30:23.000Z","msg":"前學生動源前成員何忻諾早前因涉嫌違反「港區國安法」被捕，當時獲准保釋候查，不過護照則被警方沒收。何忻諾今日於社交網站表示，警方已經將護照交還。<br />\n<br />\n何忻諾表示，警方稱會暫時釋放她，日後何忻諾無須再定期到警署報到，亦可取回保釋金和護照，但手機及電腦等財物則仍被拘查。不過警方強調，不排除日後會再將她拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n何忻諾為前學生動源的成員，她與前召集人鍾翰林、前成員陳渭賢及何諾恆先後於去年7月與10月因涉嫌違反「港區國安法」被捕，而鍾翰林目前正在還押。<br />\n<br />\n另有報道指，陳渭賢及何諾恆亦已取回護照。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/yanniloren.ho/posts/3877136285672167\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fyanniloren.ho%2Fposts%2F3877136285672167&d=nfq7Ayl5XWctTRRkLGDCS426uSpwD1fkwqqc2qDkc5E%3D&h=70e5fd2c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/yanniloren.ho/posts/3877136285672167</a>"},{"pid":"9a636ca848ca5ad7b1bb494d15a7c254f4f0b8d5","tid":2370930,"uid":13343,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T11:30:49.000Z","msg":"走啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e08568f5e06c03926e1cc793a0a6be296362c3d5","tid":2370930,"uid":76365,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T11:31:13.000Z","msg":"?咩原因還返？"},{"pid":"e8affcbd6b9ee25a18b9eb67c90d614e59ef9c6e","tid":2370930,"uid":15697,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"e08568f5e06c03926e1cc793a0a6be296362c3d5","tid":2370930,"uid":76365,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T11:31:13.000Z","msg":"?咩原因還返？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T11:32:00.000Z","msg":"應該落唔到charge？"},{"pid":"3399d5bfec29bdce015e67a8321a569a2e420abf","tid":2370930,"uid":3241,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T11:32:10.000Z","msg":"今晚就好跳上飛機啦仲等"},{"pi